title: O'Neill RG8 Comp Vest - BRET LITTLE
description: Combining eco-friendly materials with state-of-the-art features and benefits, results in a superior performance product that helps protect the environment. O'Neill continues to find real solutions to the ecological waste issues facing the surf industry today. We've been using limestone based neoprene for decades and recycling scrap neoprene for years. We are committed to making a difference with the re•generate program and its efforts to reduce, re-use, and re•generate products that keep you in the water longer.
